ed Peter from participating in the marathons alongside young men, claiming that he was embarrassing them. Also, most organizers do not care about the elderly who ran; the consideration for prize money and awards is mostly the youth. In addition to that, sponsors go for the young man. For marathons with entry fees, he sells some of the produce from his farm to facilitate his needs.
 
