•	There will be a 60-second segment titled: ‘Road Works Ahead’ and it will highlight proposed or on-going road construction or improvement projects across the country. 
•	There will be a 60-second segment titled: ‘Loading…’ which will feature the ICT advances or proposed innovations in this sphere and their predicted positive impact on society.
