This Documentary, will adopt a three structure design. In the first part the documentary will explore the world of past miss tourism winners looking into their world after the crown, second part will dwell on the current contestants, their hopes and plans for the future and finally we also plan to feature future aspirants, the young girls inspired by the initiative and are passionately  working towards winning the crown. 

