raine et les racines, un chemin different";s:6:"p_date";s:3:"130";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:8:"e_length";s:4:"9-20";s:7:"logline";s:114:"Journey of a young Man back to his roots in ruthless pursuit of essential truths to self-discovery and  freedom.
