The story will follow the structure below:

CHARACTER INTRO — The character will introduce themselves, using the format: My name is [first name], I used to be a [occupation], until ...

TITLE INTRO — This will feature Covid-related media juxtaposed with visual hints of the character's future evolution, then the title [Covid Stories]

BACKGROUND — The character will then backtrack and shed light on their background and how they ended up doing what they used to do or being who they used to be

CONFLICT — The story will then attempt to relive the moments when Covid became an inescapable reality, and how that set the character on a different path. Parallel but pertinent events relating to the character's industry and sphere will be weaved in as well to enrich the context.

PIVOT — After processing and accepting the reality, the character's new direction will take centre stage

REFLECTION — The episode will then be closed out by tying everything together and making sense of it all ... or not.";s:22:"characters_description";s:1284:"Each of the 12 episodes will focus on one individual. They are a diverse set of people with peculiar attributes that add intrigue to their story while remaining relatable by virtue of them not being celebrities or public figures.

