The story takes a shift when Garbage cartels opposed to the idea fight back by instigating war with the group. They argue that their place of work and won't allow any change. In the midst of that confrontation comes the land grabbers who grab the land and demarcate it into several hundred plots of about 80square feet to sell to public.
